Global Cake Tray Market Insights
Cake Tray Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.4% from 2024 to 2030.

Cake Tray Market Overview
The cake tray market is experiencing significant growth, with an estimated market value of approximately USD 5.6 billion in 2024 and projected to grow at a CAGR of 5.8% over the forecast period. This growth is attributed to the increasing demand for cake trays in the food and beverage industry, particularly in bakeries, supermarkets, and restaurants. The rise in disposable income, changing consumer lifestyles, and an increasing preference for ready-to-eat products are driving the market expansion. Innovations in materials and packaging technology also play a key role in the growth of this market.

